

=Bio=

"Sergio Lub is an architect, inventor, jewelry designer (www.SergioLub.com), and a social networker. He is passionate about interconnecting visionary people and in 1995, more than a decade before Web 2.0, he designed the community building freeware Friendly Favors (www.Favors.org), which is now used collaboratively by over 100 organizations, interconnecting 50,000+ people within a network of trust extending to more than 150 countries. Favors also hosts physical meetings, mostly around the San Francisco Bay Area. You can RSVP to upcoming events at: Favors.org"


